## Future Database Considerations

For production deployment with dynamic data, consider:

### PostgreSQL Schema (Future)

```sql
CREATE TABLE counties (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  medical_desert_score INTEGER,
  population INTEGER,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);

CREATE TABLE facilities (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(200) NOT NULL,
  type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  county_id UUID REFERENCES counties(id),
  latitude DECIMAL(10, 7),
  longitude DECIMAL(10, 7),
  capabilities INTEGER,
  procedures INTEGER,
  equipment INTEGER,
  has_anomaly BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);

CREATE INDEX idx_facilities_county ON facilities(county_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_facilities_type ON facilities(type);
CREATE INDEX idx_facilities_location ON facilities(latitude, longitude);
```
